<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَالثَّانِي)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لَا إذْ لَمْ يُذْكَرْ فِي الْقُرْآنِ بَدَلُهُ بِخِلَافِ غَيْرِهِ <span class="c2">(فَإِنْ قُلْنَا)</span> بِالْبَدَلِ فَفِيهِ أَقْوَالٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>